 {"id":"asupersync-1qfd0.136","title":"[audit][service] Make RateLimit::call fail closed unless readiness was observed","description":"src/service/rate_limit.rs currently returns RateLimitError::RateLimitExceeded when callers invoke call() without a preceding successful poll_ready() reservation. That conflates true token exhaustion with Service contract misuse and can trigger incorrect retry/backoff behavior upstream. Tighten RateLimit so each successful poll_ready authorizes exactly one call, introduce a dedicated typed NotReady misuse error, keep real rate exhaustion semantics intact, add focused regressions for call-without-readiness and clone-local reservation behavior, and validate with rch-backed targeted cargo commands.","status":"in_progress","priority":1,"issue_type":"bug","assignee":"DarkDesert","created_at":"2026-03-11T06:08:48.034443006Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-03-11T06:08:48.034443006Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["audit","rate_limit","service"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"asupersync-1qfd0.136","depends_on_id":"asupersync-1qfd0","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-11T06:08:48.034443006Z","created_by":"ubuntu"}]}
 {"id":"asupersync-1qfd0.137","title":"[audit][stream] Fix debounce lost wakeup when custom time_getter lags wall clock","description":"When wall-clock Sleep timer fires but custom time_getter says debounce period hasn't elapsed, the timer was cleared and Poll::Pending returned with no wake source. Buffered item stranded if upstream stays Pending. Fix: re-arm timer for remaining duration.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","assignee":"SapphireHill","created_at":"2026-03-11T07:15:40.066174166Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-03-11T07:19:37.324167628Z","closed_at":"2026-03-11T07:19:37.324143673Z","close_reason":"done","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"asupersync-1qfd0.137","depends_on_id":"asupersync-1qfd0","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-11T07:15:40.066174166Z","created_by":"ubuntu"}]}
